snippet.title: Savage gameplay (PC Game, 1988)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Savage, Dos PC game produced by Firebird Software in 1988 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/savage/12650/
I played through all three levels of this highly challenging game.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Revolution X - https://youtu.be/X41UNbdFlH4
Mortal Kombat - https://youtu.be/KwCwV6wt2IU
Earthworm Jim - https://youtu.be/enm64t_11bY
